browse
=============================

It's just a simple web server.

##Installation and usage.

    npm install
    sudo npm install iced -g
    iced index.iced 80 ~/
    #serving files from your home path (~/)



##Features

###Hide private files/directories

Put regex patterns in [.privates](.privates/) file.

###Make folder/file's icon bigger

Put regex patterns in [.bigicons](.bigicons/) file.

###Setup users as editors

Edit [.browse.config.yaml](/.browse.config.yaml) file in root path.

Example:

    users:
    - username: admin
      password: admin123

###Use another icon for folder

Edit [.icon](.icon/) file in that folder. 

Example: [view all available icons..](/css/icomoon/index.html)

    icon-cloud 
    